  "body": "### Description\nAs a Besu Dev, I want to understand Besu peering code so that we can understand current behavior, and where improvements might be made. \n\n### Acceptance Criteria\n* understand the different layers, RlpX, discovery, p2p\n* what underlying protocols are used - vertx and netty\n* process flow - what order things happen in\n* what makes a good peer vs useless peer\n* where we store peer info\n* pivot block - and how do we select which peer to download info from\n\n",
